				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-V%C4%83n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/%C4%90i%E1%BA%BFu-thi%C3%AAn-h%E1%BB%99-Gi%E1%BA%A3ng/poem-xlzt9KSVw8Lwoav4Fl9tdA">Điếu thiên hộ Giảng - 弔天護講</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-V%C4%83n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-lAWWG_aVUUofuj7GzUYcmQ">Hoàng Văn Tuấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-qu%C3%A2n/poem-CrRxrmDiaeNj-dOcA3Mp7g">Đông quân - 東君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/H%E1%BA%A1-b%E1%BA%A3n-x%C3%A3-%C4%90%C3%A0o-c%E1%BB%AD-nh%C3%A2n/poem-wTGFpGUPb82kOPAvrVJNDA">Hạ bản xã Đào cử nhân - 賀本社陶舉人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/H%E1%BB%93ng-Mao-ho%E1%BA%A3-thuy%E1%BB%81n-ca/poem-IYtTH2VHVvWxKJpemjz3fg">Hồng Mao hoả thuyền ca - 紅毛火船歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-T%C3%ADch-K%E1%BB%B3/S%C6%B0-T%E1%BB%AD-l%C3%A2m-ca/poem-2aJCr5A9EBy5oBgi4_5IIg">Sư Tử lâm ca - 獅子林歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-T%C3%ADch-K%E1%BB%B3/author-leXS2a46kBYHa9AoDh5zfw">Ngô Tích Kỳ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Th%E1%BA%A7n-Ph%C3%B9-h%E1%BA%A3i-kh%E1%BA%A9u/poem-30tYri3KEcHvKu6CPeghNw">Thần Phù hải khẩu - 神符海口</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-Thai-th%E1%BA%A1ch-l%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-v%C5%A9-h%E1%BA%ADu-quan-b%E1%BB%99c-b%E1%BB%91/poem-Vqow27pdQlBUwaSkG3-PNQ">Thiên Thai thạch lương vũ hậu quan bộc bố - 天台石梁雨後觀瀑布</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-zQyjfkM-l-eVSsp11IFYtg">Nguỵ Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Quy%E1%BB%81n/T%E1%BB%91ng-Thi%C3%AAn-S%C6%B0/poem-YaOAc36rJD4qKD7HySLfZg">Tống Thiên Sư - 送天師</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Quy%E1%BB%81n/author-dpeCK8qZl9vPtl4GNmV6lA">Chu Quyền</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%E1%BB%87p-T%C4%A9nh-Tu%E1%BB%87/T%E1%BB%91ng-Thu%E1%BB%B7-V%C3%A2n-quy-Ng%C3%B4/poem-00yIXutarjJOIoB1jKIiHw">Tống Thuỷ Vân quy Ngô - 送水雲歸吳</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%E1%BB%87p-T%C4%A9nh-Tu%E1%BB%87/author-GpDRTzqDI-ce40t-TGnLaA">Diệp Tĩnh Tuệ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu-T%E1%BA%ADp/X%C3%ADch-Th%C3%A0nh-qu%C3%A1n/poem-xeRD9N6FoIkSODBaRKpgTQ">Xích Thành quán - 赤城館</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu-T%E1%BA%ADp/author-mIUafUHZa2BMhE3Gz4w1gw">Ngu Tập</a>)<br></div>	</div>
